This game is similar in concept to angry birds. The main difference is that in angry birds you shoot one bird at a time. With this game, you place all your bombs and then detonate them with one click. If your solution did not work, it is easy to reposition your bombs and timers and click again. Same idea if you want to try again and improve your score.
